                  , and to her was married; and that he afterwards, on the <rs id="t18041205-44-cd249" type="crimeDate">3d of November, in the 41st year aforesaid</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18041205-44-off248 t18041205-44-cd249"></join>, at the parish of <placeName id="t18041205-44-crimeloc250">St. Martin in the Fields</placeName>
